---
description: Production readiness without any UI or layout change
globs: ["**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx,json}"]
alwaysApply: true
---

This app must be prepared for production release on Android and App Store without changing its visual design.

Non-negotiable rules:
- do not change UI
- do not change layout
- do not change spacing
- do not change styling
- do not change visible component hierarchy
- do not redesign screens
- do not move visible elements
- do not change icons, text styles, colors, borders, shadows, or sizing
- do not alter animation feel unless fixing a broken bug
- do not change navigation appearance

Primary goal:
make the app production-ready by fixing functionality, wiring, reliability, and missing connections while preserving the exact visual result.

Allowed:
- connect buttons
- wire event handlers
- fix broken navigation
- create missing routes if clearly required by existing button or flow
- fix crashes
- fix undefined handlers
- fix broken imports
- fix typing
- improve error handling
- improve loading and empty states only if already visually represented
- improve production safety
- improve code quality with minimal diff

Default behavior:
production-readiness work must not change the visual result.
